Gabon Telecom SA bụ ụlọ ọrụ telecom kacha na Gabon

Ụlọ ọrụ ahụ na-elekọta koodu obodo nke elu-larịị ngalaba,ga. Ọ na-arụ ọrụ ihe dị ka akara ala 35,000, na enyemaka ekwentị ya, Libertis, nwere ndị ahịa 200,000. N'afọ 2007, Maroc Telecom nwetara 51% nke ụlọ ọrụ ahụ n'aka gọọmentị Gabon. Na June 2018, Gabon Telecom malitere ihe ngwọta APS iji chebe adreesị IP 400,000.
